<h2>Single Collapsible Widget</h2>

<div id="single_collapse">
    <div data-mage-init='{"collapsible":{ "active": false, "animate": 200, "collapsible": true}}'>
        <div data-role="title">Description</div>
        <div data-role="content" style="margin : 5px; border: 1px dashed; background-color: lightgrey">
            The Magento collapsible widget converts a header/content pair into an accordion, where the content is collapsed or expanded on the header click.

            Unlike the accordion widget is that collapsible is initialized for one title/content pair, while accordion can be initialized for a set of title/contents pairs.        </div>
    </div>
</div>

